<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="section bg-paper" id="faq">
  <div class="section-wrap">
    <span class="eyebrow">FAQ</span>
    <h2 class="h2">Common <em>questions</em></h2>

    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item open">
        <button class="faq-trigger" onclick="faq(this)" aria-expanded="true">
          How much does a garage cleanout cost?
          <span class="faq-arrow">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Pricing is based on volume. Small loads start from <strong>$350</strong>, a typical full garage cleanout runs <strong>$550–$950</strong>, and larger clearances are <strong>$1,000+</strong>. Send photos for a firm upfront quote — no hidden fees.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-trigger" onclick="faq(this)" aria-expanded="false">
          Can you do same-day service?
          <span class="faq-arrow">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Yes — same-day service is often available, especially when you book before midday. We operate seven days a week across all of Greater Sydney.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-trigger" onclick="faq(this)" aria-expanded="false">
          Do I need to move my rubbish to the kerb?
          <span class="faq-arrow">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">No — you don't move a thing. You point, we load. Our team handles all lifting and carrying, whether the items are in the garage, backyard, upstairs or in storage.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-trigger" onclick="faq(this)" aria-expanded="false">
          How long does a garage cleanout take?
          <span class="faq-arrow">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Most jobs take 1–3 hours from arrival to clean-swept floor. A full garage with heavy items may take up to half a day. We give you a time estimate with your quote.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-trigger" onclick="faq(this)" aria-expanded="false">
          Is rubbish removal better than a skip bin?
          <span class="faq-arrow">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">For most homeowners, yes. You skip the heavy lifting, the week-long eyesore, the council permit, and paying for any space you didn't use. We arrive, load it all, and leave the same day.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-trigger" onclick="faq(this)" aria-expanded="false">
          Do you provide a tax invoice?
          <span class="faq-arrow">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Yes — a proper GST tax invoice is provided for every job. Useful for rental end-of-lease, estate clearances, and business claims.</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

